Author: katie23535
Text: thank you, this made me feel a little better. It's easy to invalidate yourself when you fuck up. i wanted to (liquid) fast today too but ended up eating 1578 calories which is WAY more then i've eaten since i started restricting. i'm so upset. but i'm glad i'm not the only one who's done this. stay safe love

Author: Pumpkin-butter
Text: girl I feel you.. I was planning on fasting today but impulsively decided to give myself a break (ha) eat at maintenance and I ended up eating 1500 calories in one sitting.. have been lying in bed for the last three hours in pain and regretting everything lol. we can and will get through this though <3
